Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:01:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to get into the Semi-Finals of the KC Grand Prix, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} competed with Sieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using his Goddess Combo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sieg drove Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s Monsters out of the game one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} put up a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even when faced with danger time and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he still managed to drive Sieg into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he still lost in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it really was a fantastic Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rebecca VS Leon:\N Genius Girl VS Genius Boy"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigations on Sieg Lloyd have finished, but the result was not satisfactory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the results of all his Duels have been collected...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...along with the data of him as a Duelist, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg Lloyd's background...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides his personal particulars amongst the data,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could not find any connection between him and the Schroeder family that you mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a person with such a dubious background
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,participate in so many Duel tournaments around the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, after contacting the organizers of the various competitions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we found out that at the start of each competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg would get local influential people to recommend or introduce him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that he could take part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Influential people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did try to get in touch with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they all refused to appear in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's various ways of playing such tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the name list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact this man once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that I still remember what happened back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, his attitude should change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to grab you by the tip of your tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Yugi will come and cheer me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I have to fail in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long're you gonna sit there sulking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go cheer Rebecca on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?! Rebecca this and Rebecca that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need comforting too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His deck consisted of limited edition cards that we've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already done very well, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bad news, Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You look so frantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugoroku... H-He's missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't he resting in the infirmary because his waist hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the case, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so miserable.... this hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang in there, Sugoroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll go get the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good job, Rebecca! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Great! You've done well, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh right, I need to get a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong, Mutou-{\i0}san{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sugoroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only took my eyes off him for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have gone to get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his waist hurt so badly, he couldn't possibly have gone alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Maybe someone helped him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he was abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stupid things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} say that some suspicious character snuck in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good would kidnapping Gramps do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go search for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, you go ahead first to cheer for Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we find his grandfather, we'll go cheer for Becky too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell Rebecca to do her best on our behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's split up to search for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're not coming to cheer me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi and the others still aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they running late?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I met them earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seemed like something popped up and so they might be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they said that they'd definitely come and cheer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make things difficult for them, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} asked me to tell you to do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll tolerate it for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl! Come, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as though I've turned into a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I Dueling here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulliver?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's really life-like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as though I entered a fairy tale world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got so comfortable that I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming to cheer you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}will{\i0} be coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that they'll be here slightly late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}, do you not have any family or friends coming to cheer for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're all very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm used to being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, between Rebecca and Leon, who do you think will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think Leon will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rebecca is a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Duel has attracted all these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there are so many people cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd be even better if Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0} was here to cheer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi can only cheer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Speaking of which, I wonder what happened to Sugoroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa... where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention all visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Old Man Over-Alls"is waiting for you in the ticketing booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over-alls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could that be Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that announcement just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. But I don't see the old man around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a map of Kaiba Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's this place marked with a cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it means Grandpa Sugoroku is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you all find this strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering us here on purpose so that we can see this map?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Otogi, what kind of trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know even if you asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time for the Semi-Finals to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First up, from the A Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have Sieg Lloyd versus Balfry Ginger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will be held at the planetarium special stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the B Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have Rebecca Hopkins versus Leon Wilson!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is taking place in the "Miniature Land" special stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, who will be the one to return to this final Duel Ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Semi-Finals will now... start!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Leon... come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Rebecca... do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand, I activate the Angel's Charity Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw three cards from my deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then discard two cards from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the cards I'm discarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fallen Angel Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as this card remains in the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my Life Points increase by 200 points during each of my Standby Phases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from my hand, I Summon Big Bang Girl in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will Leon-{\i0}kun{\i1} show us during this Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Forest Wolf in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forest Wolf, attack Big Bang Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Forest Wolf is quite a glutton...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it needs time to digest the food it eats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In its stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from my hand, I activate a Magic Card, Curse of Thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of Thorns...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is able to seal up effects that are activated when the Monster is in the Cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was able to destroy Rebecca's combo right from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he even stole Life Points from her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leon-{\i0}kun{\i1} will be hard to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Sapphire Dragon in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have various forms of attack.\N Allow me to teach them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sapphire Dragon, attack Forest Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sapphire Spark!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Forest Wolf got destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Monster in its stomach is Special Summoned onto the owner's field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Girl, attack the player directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the U.S. Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Glife The Phantom Bird in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Glife The Phantom Bird is a Four-Star Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It won't be able to attack if Gravity Bind is activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Glife The Phantom Bird is Summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can destroy one of my opponent's Magic or Trap Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I use Glife The Phantom Bird to attack Big Bang Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I activate the Continuous Magic, Gingerbread House, from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gingerbread House...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of card is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sapphire Dragon's Attack has increased!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being too fat is not good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During each of your Standby Phases,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gingerbread House will add 600 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, if the Monster's Attack Points exceed 2500, it'll pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my Life Points will increase by 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What card is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has many rare cards that I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand, I activate a Magic Card, The Shallow Grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us can select a Monster in our Graveyards
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Special Summon it in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Sapphire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shall revive Forest Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I sacrifice Sapphire Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Summon Emerald Dragon in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emerald Dragon, attack Glife The Phantom Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emerald Flame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really strong, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm getting all excited about this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Forest Wolf to Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from my hand, I Summon Cinderella in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Cinderella's Special Effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Pumpkin Carriage in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from my deck, I activate the Equipment Magic, Glass Slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Pumpkin Carriage is on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cinderella can attack the opponent directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cinderella, attack the opponent directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Glass Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when Cinderella attacks successfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can equip Glass Slippers on the opponent's Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster equipped with Glass Slippers cannot attack Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And its Attack Points will be decreased by 1000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I use Forest Wolf to attack Emerald Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Monster equipped with Glass Slippers is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glass Slippers will be equipped back on Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Cinderella's Attack Power will go up by 1000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These strange cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They must all be limited edition cards sold only at certain places...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I be defeated here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card from my hand, Offerings to the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By discarding one card from my hand, I can destroy one Monster on the opponent's field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I activate the Magic Card, Stamping Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can destroy one Magic Card and deal 500 points of damage to that player!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Emerald Dragon to attack Cinderella!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cinderella, Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The winner...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sieg Lloyd!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long do you\N intend to drag this on, Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think he's really in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only clue is that map.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Sugoroku, please be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Grandpa Sugoroku inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Semi-Finals of the KC Grand Prix has finally started.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Sieg secured an easy ticket into the final round...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Rebecca and Leon are locked in a fierce Duel, with neither side moving an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to go down and cheer for them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi's grandpa is trapped in a strange place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a headache this has become!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like Yugi will have to Duel someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, hang on a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Leon In Fairy Tale Land"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
